<p>
	This lovely deck of tarot cards was created by the artist Silvana Alasia who illustrates the power over the mysteries of ancient Egypt. Painted in tempera on papyrus, these cards were partially inspired by the tarot created by the famous occultist Jean-Baptiste Pitois in 1870. According to Pitois, Tarot came from the legendary Book of Thoth, a knowledgeable book which held all of the mysteries of Egyptian magic.This fantastic deck of tarot cards features 78 divining tarot cards&nbsp;in the size of 44mm x 80mm making it the perfect tool to carry in your pocket and use whenever, wherever.</p>
